HEADWORD: Basset horn
<hw>Bas"set horn`</hw> <pr>(b⟦acr⟧s"s⟦ecr⟧t h⟦ocir⟧rn`)</pr>. <ety>[See
<er>Basset</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>An
